docs {
  # Create Save

  Creates a new snapshot/save of a prompt or state.

  ## Request Body
  ```json
  {
    "title": "string (optional) - Title for the save",
    "kind": "string (optional) - Type: 'system', 'user', 'prompt', 'state' (default: 'state')",
    "provider": "string (optional) - Provider name",
    "model": "string (optional) - Model ID",
    "data": "object (optional) - Arbitrary data to save (system_prompt, user_prompt, response, parameters, notes, etc.)"
  }
  ```

  ## Response
  ```json
  {
    "id": "uuid",
    "title": "string",
    "kind": "string",
    "provider": "string",
    "model": "string",
    "created_at": "ISO 8601 timestamp"
  }
  ```
}
